                     <interp inst="t18330905-90-person929" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I turned at the moment and saw the prisoner drop the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330905-90-person930">
                  ROBERT 
                  TURLE
               <interp inst="t18330905-90-person930" type="surname" value="TURLE"></interp>
