             (City police-sergeant, No. 5). I took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was walking along and the gentleman accused me of taking his handkerchief.</p>
               <p>Mr. Morgan gave the prisoner a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 15. <rs id="t18330905-90-punish520" type="punishmentDescription">
